{"tid":406035,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"😱呢啲先係真正【地獄鬼國】😱","createTime":"2017-09-19T10:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T14:07:14.000Z","uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21cbc0aa64b73c9325ca148ad21058637ba9a968","tid":406035,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"［慎入］<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170919/bknint-20170919003227115-0919_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170919%2Fbknint-20170919003227115-0919_17011_001.html&d=uCQ6Vet1%2F7TJztx0FKYDarZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=d3163b70\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170919/bknint-20170919003227115-0919_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥上周三（13日）發現三具屍體倒臥街頭，屍身上放有當地傳統的墨西哥帽（sombrero），不過帽子所蓋着的，竟是3人的頭顱，場面驚嚇。據悉，遇害者分別是一對兄弟及其中一人的女朋友，警方懷疑他們是遭人綁架，暫時未知被殺的原因。<br />\n<br />\n27歲的萊昂（Juan Leon）、31歲的豪爾赫（Jorge Leon）及28歲的華雷斯（Yazaret Juarez）上周二（12日）於哈拉帕（Xalapa）失蹤，翌日便橫屍街頭。三人均被斬首，屍體被人用黑色垃圾膠袋及膠紙紮住，兇徒更以印有墨西哥國旗顏色的墨西哥帽包裹斷頭，充滿挑釁意味。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，陳屍地點位於當地市政廳附近，而兇手選擇的犯案時機，就在當地舉行墨西哥獨立日慶典前3天，時機十分敏感。警方目前暫時未知兇手的動機，當局日前亦發聲明譴責暴力行為，同時呼籲民眾保持冷靜，靜待調查結果出爐。<br />\n<br />\n另外，在發現屍體的同一日，哈拉帕亦有一名男子在高速公路被殺，令公眾關注安全問題。哈拉帕市長譴責暴力行為，又呼籲當地民眾保持冷靜。哈拉帕位於韋拉克魯斯州，是國內最暴力的地區，死亡率與犯罪率一直高企。<br />\n<br />\n真心多謝黨，香港人人有食有玩，仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實想睇原圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3334dace613bd871bf3f66fc161fa2a3fdfa9717","tid":406035,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:22:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6aa1ee4a42ba88c5e7f35899e2a692876a3e8b59","tid":406035,"uid":25794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:24:51.000Z","msg":"呢三條友係咪支持港獨俾何君堯殺左?"},{"pid":"48d23010f721bdf366b2e757320ca0d3e6f28796","tid":406035,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:07:14.000Z","msg":"屌，畀人騎劫咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}